headline: Eaton's Q4 Earnings on Par With Estimates, Revenues Up Y/Y
summary: ETN posts Q4 EPS in line with estimates as revenues climb 13.1% year over year, with strong Electrical and Aerospace growth offsetting weaker Vehicle results.
